Package: smlmkalman
Type: Package
Title: Functions for generating filamentous SMLM datasets and a crescent-based Kalman Filter for image segmentation.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Andrew Buist
Maintainer: ab1051@exeter.ac.uk
Description: generate_filaments() creates a dataset made to simulate those produced in DNA-PAINT imaging of plant microtubules. crescent_kf() uses a local datapoint distributions to perform Kalman Filtering on data without time information.
